name: Deluxe Business Starter Kit
description: Are you ready to get your business established with a new logo design, business card, web banner, and font + color palette style guide? Then, this deluxe business starter kit is just your size! With the purchase of this package, you will receive a custom logo design concept which we will refine to become your final logo design. Art mediums are implemented like india ink, watercolor, charcoal. Other times, illustrations are built digitally, depending on the needs of the client. All designs created are completely unique and one of kind. Here is at the most simple and easy way to understand the design process: ➳The purchase is made. ➳ I email a logo questionnaire to you which you fill out and return. ➳ I review responses and ask questions if necessary. ➳I email 1 logo design concept to you for review. ➳You will respond with edits. 3 rounds of edits are included. To read more about what the creative process involves, the turnaround time for the project and more, please read over the J+M FAQs and Policies. What logo file types are included? I include a wide variety of final files: EPS, PDF, 3 sizes of PNG files with transparent backgrounds, and 3 sizes of JPG files. I also send along an instruction sheet explaining each file type and when you should use each one. What next? If you are ready to begin the custom design process, you can purchase this listing.
